title: Dakine Women's Prom Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Women's Prom Pack in our Dylon print.
Prom Features:
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 14" laptops
- Organizer pocket
- Deployable water bottle pocket
- Insulated cooler pocket
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
